title: Mother Goose Frieze
description: Nursery or children's border with Mother Goose vignettes illustrating nursery rhymes such as old woman in shoe, Little Bo Peep, etc. Two bands to be joined printed on one strip. On brownish ground, shades of green, yellow, red, blue, white, in strong black outlines.
name: Frieze
